    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a bit scary to hear... i was hoping it was just a simple thing. but i really don't want to go to the hospital if i don't have to, it's a lot of trouble. is there really no way to just take a mild painkiller? like even a small dose of something like advil would be fine right? i just need some relief so i can get through the day.",
